Q. What are in the folder?
Txl -- source folders of the TXL grammar/transformations
bin.$(uname) -- binary built for various platforms
	bin.Darwin -- Mac OSX
	bin.Linux -- Linux
doc -- Documentations about TXL 
grammar -- user-defined grammar annotated for normalisation
	java -- Java program examples
	problem -- Problem Frames examples
result -- results
	/java -- results of Java program examples
	/problem -- results of Problem Frames examples

Q. How to compile the tool? 
% make clean
% make
